  "prompt": "What is the best and most economic perfume for men in India?",
  "response": "Choosing the best and most economical perfume for men in India often depends on personal preferences and budget. However, several options are well-regarded for their quality and affordability:\n\n1. **Wild Stone** - Known for a range of fragrant options that are affordable. Popular choices include Wild Stone Code Titanium and Wild Stone Night Rider.\n\n2. **Denver** - Offers a variety of perfumes and deodorants that are budget-friendly. Denver Hamilton and Denver Pride are good options.\n\n3. **Fogg** - This brand is renowned for its long-lasting fragrances at reasonable prices. Fogg Impressio and Fogg Marco are popular choices.\n\n4. **Park Avenue** - Offers some good options for men at an economical price. Park Avenue Euphoria and Park Avenue Original are notable mentions.\n\n5. **Engage** - Known for its wide range of fragrance options at affordable prices. Engage M1 Perfume Spray is a popular choice.\n\n6. **Nivea** - Providing good quality fragrances that are budget-friendly, Nivea Fresh Active Original is a good option.\n\n7. **Axe** - Although usually known for deodorants, Axe also has budget-friendly perfumes. Axe Signature Gold Dark Vanilla & Oud Wood Eau De Toilette is a good pick.\n\n8. **Yardley** - Offers both classic and contemporary fragrances that are economical. Yardley Gentleman Classic is a popular choice.\n\nWhen selecting a perfume, consider factors such as scent notes, longevity, and reviews from other users to ensure it suits your personal style and preferences.",
